        { "@type": "Question", "name": "What is the difference between an SEO writing tool and an SEO optimisation tool?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "A writing tool drafts the article. An optimisation tool grades and tunes it. Most modern platforms blend both — Surfer is optimisation-first with a writer; Jasper is writer-first with an optimiser bolt-on. theStacc unifies both as part of a managed pipeline." }},
        { "@type": "Question", "name": "How much should I spend on SEO content tools?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Solo SEO operations run fine on a $23–$89 seat. SMB content engines that need cadence + QA + publish are best served by an end-to-end platform like theStacc at $99/mo. Stacking three single-purpose tools usually crosses $200/mo with diminishing returns." }},
        { "@type": "Question", "name": "Can I use free SEO content tools effectively?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "For starting out, yes. RankMath (free WordPress plugin) handles on-page basics. Grammarly (free) cleans prose. Google Search Console (free) tracks ranking. The limit is operator time — free tools require you to do everything manually." }},
        { "@type": "Question", "name": "Is Surfer SEO worth it compared to cheaper alternatives?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Surfer's SERP-based scoring is still the cleanest in the market. NeuronWriter delivers most of the value at a much lower price. If you write high volume and need the best signal, Surfer earns its price. If you write occasionally, NeuronWriter is the better buy." }},
        { "@type": "Question", "name": "Do I need both a writing tool and an optimisation tool?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Most operators need both — and the cost adds up fast. End-to-end platforms (theStacc, Frase, Outranking) bundle them so you skip the integration headache. The standalone path makes sense only when you have unusual brand-voice needs." }}
      ],
      "author": { "@type": "Person", "name": "Ritik Namdev", "url": "https://thestacc.com/authors/ritik-namdev/", "sameAs": ["https://www.linkedin.com/in/ritiknamdev/"] }
    }
  ]
};
